**Summary:** Documents the Group Identify API for setting and updating group properties in Amplitude, supporting operations like $set, $setOnce, $add, $append, $prepend, and $unset on group_type and group_value parameters with limits of 5 unique group types, 10 total groups per event, and 1024 group identifies per request.

